                        "quantity_236": ",DA"
                      }
                    }
                  ],
                  "unit_combination": "(%)"
                }
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Detector efficiency was",
                "determined by studying this reaction. Deuterium gas",
                "target 0.36 mg/cm2 thick was used and relative",
                "efficiency curve was plotted covering a range of",
                "neutron energies from 1.8 to 11.3 MeV.",
                "Second time-of-flight spectrometer using a 12.5 cm",
                "diameter was used to provide the monitoring for the",
                "experiments."
              ]
            }
